					Latest News about FCX



Indonesia closer to mining deal with Freeport, but hurdles remain
JAKARTA Indonesia is closer to a deal with Freeport McMoRan Inc on its long-term future in the country, but key issues still need to be resolved before the U.S. miner gets a new operating permit for its huge copper mine, a mining ministry official said.

Jul 26 2017
UPDATE 1-Indonesia closer to mining deal with Freeport, but hurdles remain
JAKARTA, July 26 Indonesia is closer to a deal
with Freeport McMoRan Inc on its long-term future in the
country, but key issues still need to be resolved before the
U.S. miner gets a new operating permit for its huge copper mine,
a mining ministry official said.

Jul 26 2017
Indonesia, Freeport agree on term of new copper mine permit -official
JAKARTA, July 26 Indonesia has reached an
agreement with U.S. miner Freeport McMoRan Inc that any
new operating permit for its Grasberg copper mine will only be
valid until 2021, an energy and mining ministry official said on
Wednesday.

Jul 26 2017
Freeport stock soars 15 percent on copper prices, permit progress
TORONTO Freeport-McMoRan Inc shares jumped to a 16-month high on Tuesday, as soaring metal prices and progress in a long-running, costly permit dispute with Indonesia buoyed the world's biggest publicly traded copper miner.

Jul 25 2017
UPDATE 3-Freeport stock soars 15 pct on copper prices, permit progress
TORONTO, July 25 Freeport-McMoRan Inc
shares jumped to a 16-month high on Tuesday, as soaring metal
prices and progress in a long-running, costly permit dispute
with Indonesia buoyed the world's biggest publicly traded copper
miner.

Jul 25 2017
BRIEF-Freeport sees mining deal with Indonesia, but challenges -CEO
* Contract talks with Indonesia "very active", "mutual sense
of optimism" agreement can be reached -CEO Richard Adkerson

Jul 25 2017
BRIEF-Freeport-McMoRan reports Q2 adj. EPS $0.17; copper sales of 942 mln pounds
* Freeport-McMoRan reports second-quarter and six-month 2017
results

Jul 25 2017
Miner Freeport posts profit, "encouraged" by Indonesia talks
TORONTO, July 25 Freeport-McMoRan Inc
reported a second-quarter adjusted profit on Tuesday and said it
was encouraged by recent progress in talks with Indonesia to
resolve a lengthy permit dispute for its massive Grasberg mine.

Jul 25 2017
